@@ -6,6 +6,19 @@ ## Overview
 
 🚧 This project is a work-in-progress! Instructions will be added as soon as it is usable. 🚧
 
+## Contributing
+
+To contribute, please use the [Codeberg flow](https://docs.codeberg.org/collaborating/) and follow our [Code of Conduct](./CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md).
+
+To build the site locally, run:
+
+```shell
+$ git clone https://codeberg.org/pojntfx/netteart.com
+$ cd netteart.com
+$ npm install
+$ hugo server
+```
